Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.17,0:00:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.08,0:00:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not just New Himuka,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.92,0:00:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,even Seiran is full of evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.58,0:00:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,They are using human\Nbrains to make drugs!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.08,0:00:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But without the ampoule,\NI can't save my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.50,0:00:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This is 2nd Lieutenant Sumeragi's brainwave\Nwhile he was using his power.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.42,0:00:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And when we compare it with\Nthe Kunad Gate's readings...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.58,0:00:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you've made no mistake?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.33,0:00:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't be certain for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.67,0:00:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kunad Gate and Yuito's power...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.29,0:01:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,SCARLET NEXUS
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.33,0:01:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,♫A crime in reality♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.67,0:01:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,♫For Heaven's sake♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.92,0:01:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Accepts any fake♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.88,0:01:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,♫And disappears piling the eternity in fantasy♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.42,0:01:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Won't take it at all, I get sick♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.79,0:01:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,♫A girl looking back♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.83,0:01:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Casts the miracle into the instant world♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.17,0:01:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Did you lie♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.13,0:01:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Did you lie♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.00,0:01:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Spit the venom♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.13,0:01:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I know why♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.83,0:01:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I've found a game of ecstasy♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.50,0:01:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Red Criminal gets life♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.00,0:02:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I've never been in love♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.54,0:02:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Don’t know when I started\Ngetting sick of this world♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.33,0:02:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,♫We will fly♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.00,0:02:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Someday I won't be crying♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.63,0:02:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I've been sacrificing myself\Nnot to hurt anybody♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.21,0:02:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,THE TRAITOR YUITO
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.92,0:02:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The people who suggested for Seiran\Nto build that facility
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.13,0:02:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,were Karen and I.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.13,0:02:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Alice was in there, am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.75,0:02:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.08,0:02:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,She is still in her Other form.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.92,0:02:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We knew the technology would be abused.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.54,0:02:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But we persuaded Seiran into
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.29,0:02:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,building the facility.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.38,0:03:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,All that just to protect Alice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.63,0:03:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew my action was foolish.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.29,0:03:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What is going on in this country?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.75,0:03:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You conducted human experiment in Suoh,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.13,0:03:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and then you used human brains\Nto experiment on Other in Seiran...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.50,0:03:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all the more reason to take action\Nas soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.33,0:03:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Major General Fubuki, what is your action plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.58,0:03:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagi witnessed Naomi's metamorphosis.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.54,0:03:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,For research purposes, his memory\Nfrom that moment has been taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.54,0:03:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,They took his memory during the rehabilitation?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.29,0:03:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,After acquiring the data from Nagi's memory,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.79,0:03:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,we will spread it to all people\Nin this country via Arahabaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.08,0:03:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I have access to the secure site of Arahabaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.04,0:03:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.92,0:03:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is the data on Nagi's memory?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.88,0:04:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,They took his memory and damaged his brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.75,0:04:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The data is kept there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.33,0:04:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagi underwent rehabilitation over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.58,0:04:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's where they keep the files.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.54,0:04:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagi could be in there as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.75,0:04:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very likely so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.63,0:04:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure, Hanabi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.88,0:04:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.50,0:04:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But my father and uncle might know something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.13,0:04:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel just as confused as you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.00,0:04:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I've jammed the alarm system.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.00,0:04:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the information we got from\NMajor General Fubuki useful?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.13,0:04:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.33,0:04:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.50,0:04:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.46,0:04:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Alice is in here, Fubuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.88,0:04:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Arashi, Major General Karen\Nwants everyone to gather up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.58,0:05:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants all members of\Nthe Kasane Platoon present.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.79,0:05:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I got the reports from our research facility.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.83,0:05:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You let Yuito and his team escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.79,0:05:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, I am not entirely on board\Nwith Seiran's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.96,0:05:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,To turn those metamorphosed into Other\Nback to normal again,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.96,0:05:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,you allow Seiran to continue their research\Non weaponizing Other.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.88,0:05:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.08,0:05:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Even with the slightest mistake,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.50,0:05:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,those from Seiran will suspect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.63,0:05:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Please consider the risk\Nbefore you take any action.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.63,0:05:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Naomi is there. Are you sure you can save her?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.46,0:05:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,She seems to despise that drug.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.54,0:05:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.04,0:05:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Who would like drinking that stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.50,0:05:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, there is no other way\Nto save Naomi at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.71,0:06:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,By that, you mean we must force her\Nto take medicine against her will.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.50,0:06:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all he would do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.17,0:06:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you done with the speech?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.42,0:06:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No, there's one more concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.00,0:06:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We noticed a certain link with the Kunad Gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.88,0:06:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane, you must be interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.75,0:06:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, hurry up! Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.83,0:06:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yuito, it's too dangerous. Don't go there.\N-Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.00,0:06:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He has always been a stubborn kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.79,0:06:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But this time, I must make him obey
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.58,0:06:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,as a member of the Sumeragi family.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.33,0:06:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.21,0:06:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring 2nd Lieutenant to the headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.75,0:06:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.63,0:07:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.67,0:07:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, we lost contact with\N2nd Lieutenant Sumeragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.04,0:07:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The comms and brain talk didn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.42,0:07:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is he now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.54,0:07:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.63,0:07:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not his shift now,\Nso we didn't give him any mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.00,0:07:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.38,0:07:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You are allowed to use the surveillance system.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.67,0:07:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.75,0:07:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.96,0:07:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. A new security measure for Arahabaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.83,0:07:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This place doesn't look like a data center.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.04,0:07:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see any research equipment either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.13,0:07:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We must search every inch of the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.83,0:07:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll buy you some time, run while you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.21,0:07:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.75,0:07:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,He stayed to fight for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.71,0:07:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the only way back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.96,0:08:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to rescue Nagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.33,0:08:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito, you are as kind as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.50,0:08:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew you would come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.83,0:08:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, we are good friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.88,0:08:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.88,0:08:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Major General Fubuki, please come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.00,0:08:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief Sumeragi wishes to have a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.54,0:08:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He seems different now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.63,0:08:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Did they force him to\Nundergo another rehabilitation?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.17,0:08:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.42,0:08:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Personality rehabilitation?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.92,0:08:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Rehabilitation is for traitors\Nof New Himuka, like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.38,0:08:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, Nagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.29,0:09:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.29,0:09:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Team!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.21,0:09:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.46,0:09:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's happening again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.75,0:09:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I must stay conscious!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.17,0:09:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.58,0:09:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Freeze, traitors.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.00,0:09:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll demonstrate the punishment for treason
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.54,0:09:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,using this kid over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.58,0:10:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been proven the Kunad Gate was\Nlinked to Yuito's brain power.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.38,0:10:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So the future Yuito was right after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.00,0:10:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So Yuito was the cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.54,0:10:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Is killing Yuito the only solution we have?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.29,0:10:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane, don't you have something to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.21,0:10:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing I say changes anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.50,0:10:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll decide whether it's worth it or not!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.38,0:10:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't get to decide all on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.33,0:10:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You are not cute, and not to mention a show-off!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.17,0:10:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been this way since you joined the force.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.75,0:10:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But you are decisive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.54,0:10:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You complete every task with perfection.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.58,0:10:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,On that regard, I'll give you credit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.79,0:11:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.21,0:11:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I acknowledge your strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.33,0:11:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That is why we fight for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.50,0:11:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So at least have more faith in us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.79,0:11:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell us what you have in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.13,0:11:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd love to know what's bothering you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.79,0:11:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,A thought is only pointless
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.04,0:11:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,when you keep it to yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.54,0:11:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Just tell us what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.25,0:11:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We have the right to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.46,0:11:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.42,0:11:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We are a team after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.50,0:11:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.67,0:11:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you still not going to tell us?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.79,0:11:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.54,0:11:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure I could give you a clear explanation,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.58,0:11:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,so I thought it would be futile to even try.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.17,0:11:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So you have my apology.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.25,0:11:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.33,0:11:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Then just tell us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.42,0:12:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.54,0:12:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize for not being able
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.54,0:12:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,to give you a clear explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.33,0:12:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.13,0:12:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.25,0:12:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.71,0:12:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop arguing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.04,0:12:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Please tell us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.25,0:12:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Killing Yuito to prevent\Nthe destruction of our world
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.46,0:12:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,could be our only solution.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.79,0:12:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt it at the Kunad Gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.67,0:12:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You saw it too. That giant hole is growing\Nand slowly consuming the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.08,0:12:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And according to Karen,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.63,0:12:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,he knew I had been to the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.75,0:12:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And there has been scientific evidence
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.17,0:12:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,that proves the link between\NYuito and the Kunad Gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.04,0:12:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's an undeniable fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.38,0:12:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.58,0:12:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So your conclusion is that
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.96,0:12:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,we must kill Yuito to save the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.42,0:12:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're hesitating
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.58,0:12:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,because you think there could be another way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.17,0:12:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same with Naomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.63,0:13:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt we can trust Karen or Seiran.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.63,0:13:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That research facility is up to no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.42,0:13:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But we can't save Naomi by simply waiting here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.42,0:13:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's figure out a plan together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.33,0:13:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,She's right. We are comrades\Nwho trust each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.17,0:13:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,-Sorry.\N-Wrong answer, Kasane.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.75,0:13:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,There should be a different reply.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.83,0:13:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.13,0:13:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.00,0:13:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Fubuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.42,0:13:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Keep tracking them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.88,0:14:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.38,0:14:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito, you must be scared right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.67,0:14:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The examination is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.96,0:14:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Come, look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.63,0:14:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't cry, it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.79,0:14:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.21,0:14:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Our test subject is 2nd Lieutenant Sumeragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.13,0:14:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The subject is 16 years old.\NRegistration number SY567369.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.67,0:14:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Remark: "Savior of the Nation."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.46,0:14:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Use your power.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.21,0:15:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Use your power to break free from the bindings.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.92,0:15:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Brain power control system is functioning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.96,0:15:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The brain power control system is functioning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.92,0:15:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.33,0:15:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this place? Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.17,0:15:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you remember me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.29,0:15:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We've met many times in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.00,0:15:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,More precisely speaking, I had met you 17 times\N11 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.63,0:15:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You've met me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.25,0:15:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's normal you don't remember people\Nyou met in the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.96,0:15:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But as a precaution, I must validate\Nthe test subject's condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.67,0:15:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember staying in this hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.50,0:16:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There are some differences\Nin the test subject's memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.92,0:16:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not important. Where are my friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.50,0:16:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The lowered psionic hormone fixation rate\Ncould be the cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.38,0:16:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,According to the data,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.71,0:16:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,you discovered your power 11 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.04,0:16:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It was different from the modification process\Nthat of a Bell Pepper.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.88,0:16:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Bell Pepper?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.58,0:16:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The test subject doesn't remember\Never being a Bell Pepper.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.96,0:16:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I think using the brain power
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.08,0:16:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,will accumulate a certain amount of damage\Nto the subject's brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.54,0:16:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That could be the cause of his memory loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.83,0:16:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.63,0:16:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Was I a Bell Pepper?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.42,0:16:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,For those born as Bell Peppers,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.21,0:16:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,the success rate after\Nthe drug administration test is 0.5%.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.17,0:16:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Only a handful of people\Nwill become users of powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.75,0:17:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Only 0.2% of those with acquired powers
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.67,0:17:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,have abnormally strong powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.46,0:17:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But your situation is unique and unprecedented.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.96,0:17:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,For study purpose of our future plans\Nfor the Bell Peppers,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.92,0:17:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's necessary to conduct a dissection\Nto extract the brain data.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.63,0:17:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Requesting permission to dissect the subject.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.42,0:17:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.63,0:17:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanabi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.92,0:17:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Major General Fubuki, why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.54,0:17:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The program I gave you
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.83,0:17:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,was modified to stream live images.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.67,0:17:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You saved all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.83,0:17:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Nagi? Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.04,0:17:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.42,0:17:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We couldn't find his memory data either.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.21,0:17:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.88,0:17:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.38,0:17:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, everyone. Thanks for saving me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.63,0:18:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You've always saved me from danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.25,0:18:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's leave this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.33,0:18:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Our mission here
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.04,0:18:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,has been informed to the OSF.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.67,0:18:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Their soldiers will be here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.33,0:18:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I got the escape route\Nfrom Major General Fubuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.00,0:18:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The Others are coming this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.83,0:18:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We must leave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.75,0:18:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll handle the Others.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.50,0:18:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.46,0:18:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.71,0:18:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.08,0:18:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Arahabaki's password.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.33,0:18:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a terminal that can only\Nshow the password once.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.33,0:18:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you should go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.67,0:18:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I am a Septentrion.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.33,0:18:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I can clear this horde with no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.13,0:18:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Major General Fubuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.67,0:18:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to leave, Yuito.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.50,0:18:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.29,0:19:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.33,0:19:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.92,0:19:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You've become a traitor as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.33,0:19:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.08,0:19:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,"TRAITOR YUITO SUMERAGI WANTED"\NThe hero of our nation Yuito Sumeragi
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.71,0:19:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,has committed treason and is now wanted\Nby the government.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.92,0:19:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,2nd Lieutenant Yuito and his team\Ninfiltrated a government facility
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.08,0:19:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,to conduct a sabotage mission,\Nbut their mission was uncovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.92,0:19:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,As of now...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.08,0:19:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.42,0:19:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon enough, you won't be able\Nto enter Suoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.54,0:19:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Yuito?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.08,0:19:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you come to Seiran?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.33,0:19:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Seiran will welcome\Nyou and your team as ally.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.67,0:19:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You are asking me to join hands with people\Nwho use human brains for Other experiment!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.46,0:19:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,New Himuka wanted to\Ncreate stronger brain powers,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.00,0:19:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,so they conducted\Nhuman metamorphosis experiments.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.38,0:19:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Suoh was New Himuka's central city.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.75,0:20:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You are both just as wicked and insane!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.75,0:20:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you propose then?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.54,0:20:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to flee to Togetsu instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.96,0:20:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,They are an autonomous region.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.04,0:20:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps even the greatest sinners
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.04,0:20:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,would be accepted there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.08,0:20:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Togetsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.38,0:20:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,He has a point. The government wouldn't\Nattack Togetsu to get to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.33,0:20:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,They are an independent city.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.83,0:20:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, did you came all the way here\Nto tell us that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.13,0:20:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I was merely passing by.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.46,0:20:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this with you if you're going to Togetsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.25,0:20:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,-I'm not going to...\N-Whether it's human blood
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.38,0:20:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,or human brain,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.42,0:20:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,this thing will keep you alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.79,0:20:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.83,0:20:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,you will lose both your memory and your power.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.46,0:20:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This ampoule will delay the symptoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.96,0:20:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You must take it whether you like it or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.42,0:21:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.96,0:21:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up! The soldiers are coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.63,0:21:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Karen...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.50,0:21:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,They should be on the move by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.29,0:21:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you worried about something again?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.46,0:22:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, we could figure it out as a team.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.04,0:22:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.96,0:22:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it about Yuito?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.33,0:22:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Or is it about Naomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.42,0:22:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps it's both?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.00,0:22:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to stay in Seiran\Nand follow Karen's leadership?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.50,0:22:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.08,0:22:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we go to Togetsu instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.33,0:22:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I don't need to let fate dictate me♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.00,0:22:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Because I believe that I can rewrite it♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.71,0:22:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I'll always be a dreamer now and forever♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.21,0:23:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Another sunrise shines now and it blacks out♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.75,0:23:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,♫What's waiting for us at the world's end♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.83,0:23:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Forever eternal, keep the fire going♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.83,0:23:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Who can shake us♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.21,0:23:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Who can define us♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.63,0:23:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,♫It's nothing less than our story♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.58,0:23:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Forever eternal,\Nkeep the fire going in your heart♫
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.08,0:24:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,JOURNEY TO TOGETSU
